    "We evaluate on MS-COCO [36] and MJHQ-30K [31] datasets, each of which consists of image-caption pairs.",
    "Note that MS-COCO consists of realistic photos, while MJHQ-30K is constructed with images generated by Midjourney [43].",
    "We use multiple metrics to measure image quality and diversity as follows:• Diversity: LPIPS-MPD [1] computes the mean pairwise LPIPS [84] distance between images to measure perprompt diversity.",
